</a>
<h2 class="bold font-l">Jimmy Two-Shoes</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Jimmy, Beezy, and Heloise chat on their cellphones from a gazebo, a pool, and a meadow respectively. All within viewing distance of one another. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
